actions.text: Reported to Senate from the Committee on Rules and Administration (without written report).

official_title: A resolution providing for members on the part of the Senate of the Joint Committee on Printing and the Joint Committee of Congress on the Library.

summary.text: Elects the following-named Members to the following Joint Committees of Congress: Joint Committee On Printing: Mr. Cannon of Nevada, Mr. Allen of Alabama, and Mr. Scott of Pennsylvania; and Joint Committee Of Congress On The Library: Mr. Cannon of Nevada, Mr. Pell of Rhode Island, Mr. Williams of New Jersey, Mr. Cook of Kentucky, and Mr. Hatfield of Oregon.

titles.title: A resolution providing for members on the part of the Senate of the Joint Committee on Printing and the Joint Committee of Congress on the Library.
